instruction: Generate a rap song about a challenging situation.
output:

It’s a hard life, yeah it ain’t easy,
Each day I gotta get up and seize it,
Going through rough seas, the winds blowin’ freezy,
But I got faith that I’m gonna make it, come on

Chorus:
Ain’t gonna let ‘em keep me down,
Gonna stay strong and stand my ground,
The situation I’m livin’ in, never gonna keep me pinned,
Gonna spread my wings and fly and all I need is one more try

I got faith, never gonna fold my hand, no way

Chorus:
Ain’t gonna let ‘em keep me down,
Gonna stay strong and stand my ground,

Verse 3:
Fully committed, never gonna quit it,

Chorus:
